Finance and Development Commission

Meeting Schedule, Agendas and Minutes


The Finance and Development Commission (FDC) meetings include the meetings for all of the following Authorities:

  • Higher Education Building Authority (HEBA)
  • Hospital Development Authority (HDA)
  • Industrial Development Authority (IDA)
  • Residential Finance Authority (RFA)

Location & Time

Schedule

Allegheny County Economic Development 
Board Room, Suite 900 
Chatham One, 112 Washington Place  
Pittsburgh, PA 15219 


All meetings start at 9:30 AM


October 27, 2020
November 17, 2020
December 15, 2020


Please be advised that due to the Covid19 Outbreak, the October 27, November 17, and December 15, 2020 Allegheny County Hospital Development Authority, Allegheny County Residential Finance Authority, Allegheny County Industrial Development Authority & Allegheny County Higher Education Building Authority Board of Directors meetings will be held via conference call commencing at 9:30am.  The public may participate by calling toll free 1-866-398-2885 then entering access code 911114#.  Written comments should be submitted to Samuel Bozzolla by email.
